Titolo: Heavy Gear II

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: Heavy Gear II is a mecha based first-person shooter video game.  Set in Dream Pod 9's Heavy Gear universe, the game was developed and published by Activision in 1999 for Microsoft Windows; it was ported to Linux in 2000 by Loki Software. It is a sequel to the 1997 video game Heavy Gear.

Genere: First-person shooter

Valutazione: N/A
